Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.39,0:00:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}谢谢社长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.06,0:00:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}还特地陪我出来买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.80,0:00:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.89,0:00:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}需要帮忙时随时叫上我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.79,0:00:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我也能当作锻链肌肉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.13,0:00:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}话说社长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.23,0:00:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}稍微换个话题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.88,0:00:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.59,0:00:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}最近有没有在意的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.71,0:00:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}在意的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.51,0:00:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}社长对这种事没兴趣吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.78,0:00:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}也不是没兴趣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.86,0:00:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}只是由诚提起这话题 让人有点意外
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.23,0:00:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.39,0:00:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我有很多在意的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.25,0:00:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}社长也跟我说说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.83,0:00:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}又没有什么好隐瞒的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.84,0:00:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}大家都很好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.99,0:00:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}选不下手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.76,0:00:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.61,0:00:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我果然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.68,0:00:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我果然喜欢强壮树吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:00:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}你不知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.05,0:01:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那是植物型的魔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}在意的孩子是在说魔兽？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}当然 还有可能指其他事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.75,0:01:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.52,0:01:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(今天的读者来信)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.50,0:01:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(是烦恼谘询呢 标题是…)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(爱要及时！Hurry Love！ Love！！)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(听我说 我最想说的话)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.48,0:01:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(想要选择你 光凭勇气迈向梦想的你)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.64,0:01:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(这是否是个危险赌注)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.70,0:01:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(经验不足也想一同前往)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:02:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(难以预测的故事)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.15,0:02:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(是你刮起的刺激创新)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.47,0:02:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(快点！快点！带上我)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.18,0:02:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(酸酸甜甜恋爱创业)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.06,0:02:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(用规模和浪漫拉开能力差距)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(赶快！赶快！ 大胆又纤细的自我推销)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.78,0:02:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(我们的邂逅就是奇蹟)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.53,0:02:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(宇宙级的奇蹟)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.61,0:02:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(原来如此相当的沉迷呢)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.73,0:02:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(向他传达吧 就像战争般)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(爱要及时！Hurry Love！ Love！！)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(大家快点吧！Hurry Love！ Love！！)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.07,0:02:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}然后啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.59,0:02:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}似乎在迷宫深处遇到了魔兽群
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.41,0:02:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那还真是不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.93,0:02:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}之后怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.93,0:02:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}他们想要无视那群魔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}却发生了惊人的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.96,0:03:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.02,0:03:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}然后呢然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}惊人的事件是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}魔兽竟然对那冒险者说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}骗人 有那种魔兽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.72,0:03:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.91,0:03:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}传言说是不是新品种魔兽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那还真想看看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}真惊人的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}听说有只会说人话的魔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是玛莉卡小姐听来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不过说人话的魔兽之前也有遇到过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.66,0:03:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}假日出勤…加班…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}裁员…成就感…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}说起来那群魔兽 被黑心上司强迫工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.33,0:03:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不是那种喃喃自语
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.55,0:03:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}听说能确实跟魔兽沟通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}大家知道法姆涅拉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.91,0:03:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}记得是人型的魔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:04:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}听说拥有相当高的智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}听说有只法姆涅拉会流畅地说人话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那的确很稀奇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}绝对是新品种啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}社长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.74,0:04:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我想…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我想看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我想见见它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.74,0:04:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}见见那只法姆涅拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}真起劲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}它会说人话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.29,0:04:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}可以跟人类沟通
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}进入奇怪的模式了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}好想见它…好想见它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}诚？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}大家也赶快过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这病得很重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:05:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}就算是我弟弟 我也跟不上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.97,0:05:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}也不能放诚一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我们也去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}社长真的是烂好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不用硬陪着他走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.94,0:05:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我也有点好奇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}之前出现了机械迷宫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}现在出现了说人话的魔兽…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}说不定这也跟爸爸前往调查的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}大型门的影响有关
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}快一点快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}大家太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.16,0:05:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}连新装备都忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}连诚的装备都要搬过来 可辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}搬的人是社长就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}尤托利亚也带上武器了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}话说 真不愧是各位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:05:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这些装备真合身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}社长嘴真甜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.97,0:06:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}说这种一目了然的客套话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.23,0:06:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}赞我们也没什么好处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.90,0:06:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我不是这意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}怎样都好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.15,0:06:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}快点出发啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.41,0:06:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}社长 走罗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.26,0:06:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}魔兽比我们还重要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}抱歉 我不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}找不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.13,0:06:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}诚 稍微冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}目标法姆涅拉都要被你吓跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.07,0:06:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.39,0:06:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}记得法姆涅拉是会群聚的种族
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}首先要找到他们的群落…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.01,0:06:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}对了！我想到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.86,0:06:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}只要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}有大量的脚步声
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}好厉害！这样都听得出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}若有似无的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:07:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我的魔兽爱一定会告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是这边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.55,0:07:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是哪边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是这边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}诚 等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}走这么快会跌倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}才刚说完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.95,0:07:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}大家 看看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.28,0:07:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那是光水晶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.43,0:07:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}还真稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}在迷宫中途就发现光水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}你看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.77,0:07:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}似乎不只如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.17,0:07:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}有各种类型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}法姆涅拉最喜欢这种亮晶晶的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.11,0:07:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}所以这附近一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.01,0:07:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}诚！那边！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是法姆涅拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.08,0:07:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}数量还挺多的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.83,0:07:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}大家 先谨慎的观察状…况…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}你会说话吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.32,0:08:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我叫做诚！听得懂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我们做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.99,0:08:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}安心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}你看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}诚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}诚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}笨蛋 你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}姐姐才是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}你看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.51,0:08:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}看什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}战意满满呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}在受伤前击退他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}社长请下指示
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}毕竟不是对面主动打过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}随意开战说不定新品种也会逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}只要打跑它们就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}该我出场了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.53,0:08:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.31,0:08:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我是第一次见到法姆涅拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.75,0:08:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}还真的长得跟人类一模一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.15,0:08:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}它们会避开不必要的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.03,0:09:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这点也很像人类
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.94,0:09:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}法姆涅拉本来就是聪明的魔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}会群聚一起行动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}也会协力进行攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}作为敌人还真麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.94,0:09:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}的确
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}诚也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.31,0:09:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}之后的行动还请谨慎些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我有点失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.47,0:09:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}对不起 我之后会更冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.99,0:09:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那是奈欧隆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.89,0:09:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}诚？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}你看！有这么多！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}奈欧隆是特殊的药草
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.31,0:09:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}可以当作回复魔法使用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}马上又失控了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是这样啊 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.17,0:09:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}诚 适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.26,0:09:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我也是名冒险者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}之后就会冷静的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.34,0:09:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是水晶花！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是非常贵重的植物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.91,0:09:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:10:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}传说只要获得它就会有好运上门
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}好想要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}颤抖不已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}等等 诚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这附近地盘不太安定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}要小心…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}诚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}他晕过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}回去的路…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}尤托利亚 朱莉小姐 玛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.19,0:10:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我一个人可搬不动诚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.55,0:10:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.62,0:10:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}它动了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.48,0:11:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.13,0:11:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}走投无路了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}诚！社长！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.18,0:11:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}看来一路延伸到深处了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.37,0:11:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}社长…诚…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}事到如今
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}只能找出前往下方的路了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.32,0:11:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.05,0:11:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}毕竟这样下去 诚阁下也危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那个背包是员裁草那时的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.23,0:12:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}难咬得要命还没什么味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.26,0:12:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}一点都不好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}全都吃下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.91,0:12:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}就当作什么都没看到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.27,0:12:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}它在看着这边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}社长阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}有听见吗？社长阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.85,0:12:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不用这么害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}在下意外地喜欢社长阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.02,0:13:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那个 你到底是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}在下是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}只是个背包
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那还真是有点牵强
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.32,0:13:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不管怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.24,0:13:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}诚阁下非常重视"希望企业"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.58,0:13:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}虽然他热衷于某件事时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.41,0:13:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}会顾不上周遭状况
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.47,0:13:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}但他很纯粹 很直率 是个内心温柔的青年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.84,0:13:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}之后也请社长阁下 多多关照诚阁下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.99,0:13:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}诚 你醒来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}记得我摔进洞穴里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}你就晕过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.07,0:13:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}社长还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.49,0:13:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}没被魔兽袭击吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}完全没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.50,0:14:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.53,0:14:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}都是我的错才害社长也遇上危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}没这回事 不要太在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.14,0:14:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不过的确希望你不要太过莽撞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我在反省了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}身为一名冒险者 身为"希望"的社员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我会更加沉着冷静地行动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.47,0:14:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}诚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.35,0:14:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}果然纯粹又直率 内心还很温柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不过接下来该怎么办呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}想要跟其他人会合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这边看起来是爬不上去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.61,0:14:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}只好找找其他道路了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.51,0:15:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}尤托利亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}社长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}诚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.70,0:15:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不在的话就回声不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}真不该找什么会说话的法姆涅拉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}没想到我们会就这样失去社长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}别乌鸦嘴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.82,0:15:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}别看社长那样 他的生命力可好比蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.39,0:15:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}有东西动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.12,0:15:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}蟑螂社长？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不要把两个词接在一起说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.44,0:15:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.50,0:15:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我们是"希望企业"的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}名片正好用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}可以请教一下尊姓大名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我叫米涅子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.49,0:16:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这下安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.46,0:16:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}没想到除了我们还有其他冒险者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.96,0:16:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我是社长 凑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.16,0:16:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这位是社员 诚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.36,0:16:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}敝社公司规模并不大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.25,0:16:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}但是万事皆全社同心协力…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.85,0:16:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}社长 不用这么毕恭毕敬的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.91,0:16:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}其实我们跟其他社员走散了 现在正困扰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}如果您知道的话 可以告诉我们向上的路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我们绝对不是可疑分子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.69,0:16:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}往这边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.51,0:16:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}太好了 诚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那边 注意头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那边 容易崩塌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}你很熟悉道路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.57,0:17:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}曾经攻略过这迷宫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这是商业机密呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.83,0:17:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不够机灵 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这边 爬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}就能到 上面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}万分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.96,0:17:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}真的是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}日后希望能到府上再次致谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}能请教贵公司的住址或联络方式…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.05,0:17:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不用 道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我们想好好道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}能让我们看看你的脸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.11,0:18:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.79,0:18:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不用害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}法姆涅拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不过跟一般的法姆涅拉有些不同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}而且刚刚他讲话了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}难道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这就是传说中会说人话的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}果然是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}诚 你注意到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}一开始见面时就在想着是不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}原本是想要立刻确认的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}但是我已经说好要谨慎行事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}带完路了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}马上 离开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.62,0:18:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}等等 你受伤了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不介意的话能让我看看伤口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.66,0:18:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我是僧侣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}回复魔法是家常便饭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.04,0:18:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}只要这边这样做…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.02,0:18:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我要抹上奈欧隆了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}痛楚马上就会消散了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.48,0:19:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}之后缠上绷带
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.97,0:19:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}还有地方会痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}多管 闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.38,0:19:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}米涅子 这样 就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}怎么这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.74,0:19:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.80,0:19:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}好像做了多余的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我一直在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.26,0:19:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}就是为了见你一面才来这座迷宫的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}所以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.80,0:19:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不介意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}能成为我的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}朋 友？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我想要进一步了解米涅子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.35,0:20:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}朋友 人类 和 米涅子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.87,0:20:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}没错 朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}你这魔兽！快离开诚身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.14,0:20:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}米涅子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.34,0:20:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}还真危险呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}可要好好告诉你姐姐 说我救了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.24,0:20:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}你都做了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}是吧是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.66,0:20:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}大病初愈就能挑战魔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.37,0:20:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这可不是简单的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}你看你都做了什么好事！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}难得我们要交上朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}诚 没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.86,0:20:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.56,0:20:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我担心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.09,0:20:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}对不起 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那个 朱莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:20:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}为什么莱巴先生也在？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.62,0:20:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}那东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}不要叫我"那东西"啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.52,0:21:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}在寻找诚跟社长时 碰巧遇上他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}他似乎正在单独探索
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}就请他帮忙找人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.34,0:21:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}这样啊 不好意思让你们担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}诚没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.72,0:21:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}都不向本大爷道谢的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.15,0:21:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.31,0:21:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我…我想…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我想去追米涅子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.91,0:21:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}米涅子？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.51,0:21:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}我想再跟他说一次话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.39,0:21:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}然后跟米涅子交上朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.19,0:22:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(抬头仰望 夜空中)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.42,0:22:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(发现了美丽的宝石)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(希望明天也能放晴)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.40,0:22:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(向星星许愿)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.60,0:22:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(缓缓的 今天迈向结束)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.42,0:22:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(拖着疲惫的身体)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.02,0:22:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(辛苦了)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.49,0:23:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(明天再加油吧)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.43,0:23:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(晚安)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.73,0:23:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(每天都闪耀动人)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.44,0:23:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(就像宝石盒一般)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.81,0:23:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(光彩炫目)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(还没做完的事)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.27,0:23:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(就在梦中继续)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.73,0:23:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(出发冒险吧)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.94,0:23:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(今晚好好休息)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.43,0:23:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\shad0}(在梦中与你相会)

